api id | x31o4vkvkd | sbi671ftua | 6j3slogml9 | yigga7p8jk  | 8ctmv1lwyb |

### Endpoints
```
/authorize             GET  -> lambda -> backend-api-authorize:live
/redirect              GET  -> lambda -> backend-api-redirect:live
/token                 POST -> lambda -> backend-api-token:live

/error                 GET  -> s3     -> backend-api-authorize-error-${env}/{lng}/authorize-error.html
/assets/{fileName+}    GET  -> s3     -> backend-api-authorize-error-${env}/assets/{fileName}
/.well-known/jwks.json GET  -> s3     -> sts-backend-api-jwks-${env}/.well-known/jwks.json
```
